s commonly used to capture filtering decisions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements."}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/OUDSTheme":{"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"This is a basic theme any theme must be a subclass off, or all themes must have as ancestor.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A Swift ","type":"text"},{"code":"class","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" has been used so as to allow to easily override some attributes and have inheritance, without having for developers","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to implement all tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any properties of an overridable theme should be defined so as to provide defaults values."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"We allow this theme to be derivated and be overriden."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" can be seen as a kind of “abstract class” in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"object oriented paradigm"}]},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme contract"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type"